  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Jump to:</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#whatdoineedtodo\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What do I need to do? </span></a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#H2\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What information do I need to provide?</span></a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#H3\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What information does Back Market report to tax authorities? </span></a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#DoIneedtopaytaxesonmyincome\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Do I need to pay taxes on my income? </span></a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#WherecanIfindmyTaxIdentificationNumber\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Where can I find my Tax Identification Number (TIN)? </span></a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#WhathappensifIdontprovidemyinformation\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What happens if I don’t provide my information? </span></a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#Whatsthelegalbasis\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What&#39;s the legal basis for data collection under the DAC7 directive?</span></a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#Whowillreceivemyinformation\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Who will receive my information? </span></a></span></strong></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;font-weight: bold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"#Howlongwillmyinformationbekept\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">How long will my information be kept on record?</span></a></span></strong></li></ul>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: rgb(41, 128, 185);font-weight: bold;\"> </p>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">DAC7 is a European Union (EU) directive that requires online marketplaces like Back Market to: </span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Collect and verify certain tax information concerning sellers that are established in the EU</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Report the income of these sellers who reach a specific sales or revenue limit to the tax authorities</span></li></ul>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">If this applies to you, you&#39;ll need to provide your taxpayer details and confirm your business information in the Back Office.<br><br>Back Market must report tax information by 31 January of each year, for sales of the previous calendar year.</span><br><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"whatdoineedtodo\" name=\"whatdoineedtodo\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>What do I need to do? </strong></a></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">If your business is established in the EU and meet one of the following conditions, are in the scope of DAC7: </span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">You made 30 or more sales in the past calendar year.</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">You&#39;ve earned more than 2,000.00 € from your Back Market sales over the past calendar year.</span></li></ul>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">If you are in the scope of DAC7, you are required to verify that your seller information in the Legal Details and Tax Details sections of your Back Office is correct, accurate and up to date.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"H2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #000000;\"></a>What information do I need to provide?</span></strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">You need to provide and verify the information on your seller Back Office about your business details and most importantly, the following information:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Legal name/registered company name</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Main address</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Company identification number </span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Tax identification number (NIF/TIN of your country of establishment)</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">VAT number (if applicable)</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Presence of a permanent establishment in another country within the EU.  </span></li></ul>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a id=\"H3\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #000000;\"></a>What information does Back Market report to tax authorities? </span></strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Back Market is required to report your business details (such as name, address, TIN, VAT number) and to verify this information. Back Market is also required to report, for each seller : </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Amount of consideration paid for sales of products on Back Market, per quarter </span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Number of sales per quarter </span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Back Market fees and potential taxes paid by Back Market on your behalf. </span></li></ul>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"DoIneedtopaytaxesonmyincome\" name=\"DoIneedtopaytaxesonmyincome\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Do I need to pay taxes on my income? </strong></a></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"> If you sell products on Back Market, you may be subject to tax and social security requirements in one or several countries of the EU, particularly in regard to Value-Added Tax (VAT) and income/corporate tax. <br><br>It&#39;s your responsibility to check your tax and social security requirements and comply with any applicable regulations.<br><br>For more information, please contact the tax authorities, your accountant, or your tax advisor.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">The DAC7 report does not determine your tax liability. Even if Back Market reports your sales under DAC7 requirement, you still have to report and pay your taxes. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"WherecanIfindmyTaxIdentificationNumber\" name=\"WherecanIfindmyTaxIdentificationNumber\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Where can I find my Tax Identification Number (TIN)? </strong></a></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"> Your Tax Identification Number (TIN) is assigned to your business by the tax authorities in your country of establishment. <br><br>If you don&#39;t know where to find your Tax Identification Number (TIN), contact the tax authorities in your country of establishment. For information purposes only, we&#39;ve compiled some information about Tax Identification Numbers (TINs) in each country within the EU:</span><br><br><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<table border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Country</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Name of Tax Identification Number (TIN)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Format</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">France</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">SIREN number</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">9 digits (example: 999 999 999)</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Germany</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Steuernummer (Tax Identification)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">10–13 digits (most often 10 digits)</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Spain</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">NIF (Numero de Identification Fiscal)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">9 digits or letters starting with a letter </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Ireland</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Tax Reference Number (TRN)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">7 digits + either 1 or 2 letters </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Cyprus</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Tax Identification Number (same as VAT)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">9 digits or letters<br>(8 numbers followed by a letter) </span></p>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Netherlands</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Tax Identification Number</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">9 digits </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Italy </span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Codice Fiscale <br>Tax Identification Number</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">11 digits </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Lithuania</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Tax Identification Number </span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">9 or 10 digits </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Estonia </span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Registration Code <br>Tax Identification Number</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">8 digits </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Belgium</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Numéro d’Identification de l’Entreprise <br>Numéro d’Entreprise Belge (Ondernemingsnummer)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">10 digits </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Austria</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Steuernummer</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">9 digits (example: 999 999 999)</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">  </span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"WhathappensifIdontprovidemyinformation\" name=\"WhathappensifIdontprovidemyinformation\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>What happens if I don’t provide my information? </strong></a></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">If you provide incorrect or incomplete information or fail to provide it at all, Back Market may have to suspend your payouts and your activity on the platform.</span><br><br><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"Whatsthelegalbasis\" name=\"Whatsthelegalbasis\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>What&#39;s the legal basis for data collection under the DAC7 directive?</strong></a> </span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The data collected by Back Market to comply with the DAC7 Directive (Council Directive (EU) 2021/514) is required by law (article 1649 ter A et seq. of the French General Tax Code).</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"Whowillreceivemyinformation\" name=\"Whowillreceivemyinformation\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Who will receive my information? </strong></a></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Back Market report all information collected to French tax authorities, in accordance with a secure procedure imposed by those authorities.<br><br>The French tax authorities may exchange this information with tax authorities in other EU countries.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><a id=\"Howlongwillmyinformationbekept\" name=\"Howlongwillmyinformationbekept\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>How long will my information be kept on record?</strong></a></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Your information will be kept for as long as is necessary for Back Market to comply with the DAC7 directive.</span></p>"
}